==Finnish==

===Derivational suffix===
'''-e'''

# Used for forming nouns from verbs or adjectives.
#:''[[ottaa]]'' "to take (hold of)" -> ''[[ote]]'' "grip"
#:''[[paha]]'' "bad, evil" -> ''[[pahe]]" "vice"
#:''[[ääntää]]'' "to pronounce, enunciate" -> ''[[äänne]]'' "sound (in phonetics)"

