==Hungarian==
===Suffix===
'''-e'''

# Suffix for yes/no questions.  Not needed for all such questions: in most case a question is indicated only by emphasis and question mark.  Always attached to the main word (usually the verb) of the [[predicate]] of the prhase.  Always written with a hyphen before.
#: '''1857:''' Arany János, A walesi bárdok
#:: Van-e ott folyó és földje jó? <br> &emsp; Legelőin fű kövér <br> Használt-e a megöntözés: <br> &emsp; A pártos honfivér?
